        en: >-
          This postcard for winter 2026 looks more like a poster than a
          postcard. With the distorted portrait of the woman and the striking
          text, it leans towards the psychedelic art style. The colours blue and
          red were, of course, deliberately chosen, as their warm-cool contrast
          reflects the winter outside and inside.
