        en: >-
          The 2025 summer menu captures the very best of a hot summer’s day: a
          cool drink.

          The orange-coloured Aperol-style cocktail, with its slice of lemon and
          three-dimensional ice cubes, brings that refreshing sensation right
          into your hand. In contrast, the blue sky visible through the glass,
